(ns ui.components.positions
  (:require [reagent.core :as r]
            [re-frame.core :as rf]
            [reitit.frontend.easy :as rfe]
            [ui.subs :as subs]
            [ui.events :as events]
            [ui.components.charts :as charts]))

(defn format-currency [amount]
  (when amount
    (.toLocaleString amount "en-US" #js {:style "currency" :currency "USD"})))

(defn positions-table [positions]
  [:div.table-responsive
   [:table.table.table-hover.position-table
    [:thead
     [:tr
      [:th "Instrument"]
      [:th "Type"]
      [:th "Units"]
      [:th "Entry Price"]
      [:th "Current Price"]
      [:th "Value"]
      [:th "P&L"]]]
    [:tbody
     (for [position positions]
       ^{:key (:instrument position)}
       [:tr
        [:td [:a {:href (rfe/href :instrument-detail {:id (:instrument position)})}
              (:instrument position)]]
        [:td (:type position)]
        [:td (:units position)]
        [:td (format-currency (:entry-price position))]
        [:td (format-currency (:latest-price position))]
        [:td (format-currency (:current-value position))]
        [:td {:class (if (pos? (:pl position)) "positive-value" "negative-value")}
         (format-currency (:pl position))]])]]])

(defn position-type-tab [type active-type on-change]
  [:li.nav-item {:role "presentation"}
   [:button.nav-link
    {:class (when (= active-type type) "active")
     :id (str type "-tab")
     :data-bs-toggle "tab"
     :data-bs-target (str "#" type)
     :type "button"
     :role "tab"
     :aria-controls type
     :aria-selected (= active-type type)
     :on-click #(on-change type)}
    (clojure.string/capitalize type)]])

(defn positions-view []
  (let [positions @(rf/subscribe [::subs/positions])
        all-positions-count (count positions)
        forex-positions @(rf/subscribe [::subs/positions-by-type "forex"])
        crypto-positions @(rf/subscribe [::subs/positions-by-type "crypto"])
        other-positions @(rf/subscribe [::subs/positions-by-type "other"])
        [active-tab set-active-tab] (r/atom "all")]
    [:div
     [:h1.my-4 "Trading Positions"]
     [:div.card.mb-4
      [:div.card-header.d-flex.justify-content-between.align-items-center
       [:h5.mb-0 "Positions Overview"]
       [:button.btn.btn-sm.btn-outline-primary.refresh-btn
        {:on-click #(rf/dispatch [::events/fetch-positions])}
        [:i.bi.bi-arrow-clockwise] " Refresh"]]
      [:div.card-body
       [:div.row.mb-4
        [:div.col-md-3
         [:div.metrics-tile
          [:h6 "Total Positions"]
          [:h3 all-positions-count]]]
        [:div.col-md-3
         [:div.metrics-tile
          [:h6 "Forex Positions"]
          [:h3 (count forex-positions)]]]
        [:div.col-md-3
         [:div.metrics-tile
          [:h6 "Crypto Positions"]
          [:h3 (count crypto-positions)]]]
        [:div.col-md-3
         [:div.metrics-tile
          [:h6 "Other Positions"]
          [:h3 (count other-positions)]]]]

       (when positions
         [charts/positions-pie-chart positions])

       [:ul.nav.nav-tabs.mb-3 {:id "positionsTab" :role "tablist"}
        [position-type-tab "all" @active-tab set-active-tab]
        [position-type-tab "forex" @active-tab set-active-tab]
        [position-type-tab "crypto" @active-tab set-active-tab]
        [position-type-tab "other" @active-tab set-active-tab]]

       [:div.tab-content {:id "positionsTabContent"}
        [:div.tab-pane.fade
         {:class (when (= @active-tab "all") "show active")
          :id "all"
          :role "tabpanel"}
         (if positions
           [positions-table positions]
           [:p "Loading positions..."])]

        [:div.tab-pane.fade
         {:class (when (= @active-tab "forex") "show active")
          :id "forex"
          :role "tabpanel"}
         (if forex-positions
           [positions-table forex-positions]
           [:p "Loading forex positions..."])]

        [:div.tab-pane.fade
         {:class (when (= @active-tab "crypto") "show active")
          :id "crypto"
          :role "tabpanel"}
         (if crypto-positions
           [positions-table crypto-positions]
           [:p "Loading crypto positions..."])]

        [:div.tab-pane.fade
         {:class (when (= @active-tab "other") "show active")
          :id "other"
          :role "tabpanel"}
         (if other-positions
           [positions-table other-positions]
           [:p "Loading other positions..."])]]]]]))
